Show HN: A clean crypto price and news terminal
text:
A few friends and I were discussing how frustrated we were at how messy crypto price websites are. Flooded with adverts and designed to increase time on site, we decided to do the opposite.

We created DefiDive so that the information users wanted would be displayed as quickly as possible in a clean interface. Our news section is designed to pull in a list of major crypto news sources, YouTube and Twitter accounts and have a filterable view based on the cryptos you are interested in.

https://defidive.com/news

This is just the start, we would love feedback from the HN community on how we can help you ease the pain in your crypto related daily workflow.

What additional features would you like?
